Subject: || UNABLE TO SET UP ON_PREMISE SERVER - MPS LIMITED- 17032025 ||
Description:
Dear Team,

Unable to set up the server -on premise. Kindly do the needful.
What_We_Know__c:
In our call earlier, the issue we discovered is that the customer used an old version of VMwarePlayer, after installing version 17 they were able to successfully deploy the Endpoint Protector virtual appliance.
​​​​​​
Next_Steps__c: Issue is resolved, this case can be closed.
